OL,3,CMajor manhunt after car crash leaves
OL,4,Cseveral people injured in town centre
OL,6,FA major manhunt is underway for a
OL,7,Fsuspect after multiple pedestrians
OL,8,Fwere injured in a suspected hit-and-
OL,9,Frun by a car in a Nottinghamshire town
OL,10,Fcentre.
OL,12,FNottinghamshire Police said the hit-
OL,13,Fand-run incident occurred in Market
OL,14,FPlace, Arnold, at 1.12am today (May 9).
OL,16,FA number of people were struck by the
OL,17,Fvehicle, a red Vauxhall Astra, with
OL,18,Fone of the victims sustaining life-
OL,19,Fthreatening injuries.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G1/5
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
