OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,375,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37402
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F374A1778361067
OL,3,CMajor manhunt after car crash leaves
OL,4,Cseveral people injured in town centre
OL,6,FThe vehicle was abandoned at the
OL,7,Fscene, and the driver fled on foot.
OL,9,FDetectives said they have identified a
OL,10,Fsuspect - believed to be a white man -
OL,11,Fand are in the process of tracking him
OL,12,Fdown.
OL,14,FSeveral road closures are in place
OL,15,Faround Arnold town centre as police
OL,16,Finvestigate the incident.
OL,18,FMarket Place, as well as the junctions
OL,19,Ffrom Gedling Road to Derby Street,
OL,20,FHallam's Lane and Central Avenue are
OL,21,Fclosed off.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G2/5
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,375,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37403
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F374A1778361067
OL,3,CMajor manhunt after car crash leaves
OL,4,Cseveral people injured in town centre
OL,6,FPolice said the closures will remain
OL,7,Fin place for some time and have urged
OL,8,Fmotorists to avoid the area where
OL,9,Fpossible.
OL,11,FAnyone who witnessed the incident or
OL,12,Fhas information relating to what
OL,13,Fhappened is urged to share it with the
OL,14,Fpolice.
OL,16,FDCI Ruby Burrow, of Nottinghamshire
OL,17,FPolice, said: "There is no indication
OL,18,Fat this stage of any ongoing threat to
OL,19,Fthe wider public.
OL,26,@yD@OOU
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G3/5
