OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,375,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37404
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F374A1778361067
OL,3,CMajor manhunt after car crash leaves
OL,4,Cseveral people injured in town centre
OL,6,F"However, we understand the incident
OL,7,Fwill cause concern in the community.
OL,9,F"Officers will remain at the scene
OL,10,Ftoday to carry out further inquiries,
OL,11,Fspeak to local people and offer
OL,12,Freassurance.
OL,14,F"It is also important that anyone with
OL,15,Finformation, or relevant dashcam,
OL,16,FCCTV, doorbell or mobile phone
OL,17,Ffootage, gets in touch without delay."
OL,19,FInformation can be shared with police
OL,20,Fby calling 101, quoting incident 46 of
OL,21,FMay 9.
OL,26,@nD@AOUqD@AOUvD@AOUyD@fO]
